                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "The number ten corresponds to the ten fundamental aspects of the Creator's desire to bestow. Just as the decimal system underlies all mathematics, the ten Sefirot form the complete structure through which all spiritual reality is organized.",
