                          "name": "t4p1",
                          "fill": "$body-text",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Know that before the emanated beings were created, the Simple Infinite Light (Ohr Ein Sof) filled all of existence. There was no vacant space, no empty air, nothing — only the Simple Infinite Light.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.75,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "hmrXJ",
                          "name": "t4p2",
                          "fill": "$body-text",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "When it arose in the Thought of the Simple Light to create the worlds and emanate the emanations, in order to reveal His perfection to His creations, He then contracted Himself (Tzimtzum) in the point of the center of His light.",
                          "lineHeight": 1.75,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 14,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
