                      "content": "Know that before the emanated beings were created, the Simple Infinite Light (Ohr Ein Sof) filled all of existence. There was no vacant space, no empty air — only the Simple Infinite Light.",
                      "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
