                      "fill": "$body-text",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Baal HaSulam emphasizes that this is not a spatial contraction but a restriction of the Creator's will to bestow — making room for the will to receive that defines all created beings.",
